channel.title: Help me please if you can
channel.description:
Hello, i have a westell model e90-610030-06 router and for some reason i have port forwarded and everything but i can't put my server on the online status thing says it is offline when i have it running
If you can help please add me on msn if you have it at (criptscape@hotmail.com) i need the help really bad atm, ive tried for 3 months to get it to work
and i also baught a new linksys router model wrt150n, i tried to set it up but after i did i plugged my dsl into it and it wouldnt work.
If this is against rules to ask for help here then tell me and i will delete. thanks[br][size=1]Posted on: September 29, 2007, 04:40:50 PM[/size][hr]come on people. =[
